---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Staticfish" description="Privacy Policy for Staticfish web development services.">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col overflow-x-hidden">
    <Header />
    <main class="flex-1 pt-32">
        
        <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
            
            <div class="mb-16">
                <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">Legal</span>
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tighter text-slate-900 sm:text-6xl mb-6">
                  Privacy Policy
                </h1>
                <p class="text-slate-600 font-medium">Last updated: January 2025</p>
            </div>

            <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-600">
                
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Introduction</h2>
                <p class="mb-6">
                    Staticfish ("I", "me", "my") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how I collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit my website or use my services.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Information I Collect</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Information you provide:</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Name and contact information (email, phone)</li>
                    <li>Business information</li>
                    <li>Project requirements and specifications</li>
                    <li>Payment information (processed securely via Stripe)</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-4"><strong class="text-slate-900">Automatically collected information:</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>IP address</li>
                    <li>Browser type and version</li>
                    <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
                    <li>Referring website</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">How I Use Your Information</h2>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>To provide and maintain my services</li>
                    <li>To communicate with you about your project</li>
                    <li>To process payments</li>
                    <li>To improve my website and services</li>
                    <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Data Storage and Security</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    I take data security seriously. Your information is stored securely using industry-standard encryption and security measures. I use Cloudflare for website security and Stripe for secure payment processing. I never store your credit card information.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Third-Party Services</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4">I use the following third-party services:</p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Cloudflare</strong> - Website hosting and security</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Stripe</strong> - Payment processing</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-slate-900">Email service providers</strong> - Communication</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    These services have their own privacy policies and may collect data according to their terms.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Cookies</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    My website uses minimal cookies for essential functionality and analytics. You can control cookie settings through your browser.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Your Rights</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-4">Under GDPR and UK data protection laws, you have the right to:</p>
                
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Access your personal data</li>
                    <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
                    <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
                    <li>Object to data processing</li>
                    <li>Request data portability</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="mb-6">
                    To exercise these rights, email me at contact@staticfish.co.uk
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Data Retention</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    I retain your information for as long as necessary to provide services and comply with legal obligations. Project-related data is typically retained for 2 years after project completion.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Changes to This Policy</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. I will notify you of any significant changes by email or through a notice on my website.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6">Contact Me</h2>
                
                <p class="mb-6">
                    If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or how I handle your data, please contact me:
                </p>
                
                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-2xl mb-12">
                    <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Staticfish</p>
                    <p class="mb-1">Email: contact@staticfish.co.uk</p>
                    <p>Data Controller: Michael Fisher</p>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </main>
    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
